snippet.title: Pure Sweat Project
snippet.description: My dance, fitness and nutrition project.  I spent two years dancing for the NBA OKC Thunder Girls and have  transitioned from there to a new stay-at-home mom and cardio dance fitness instructor.  I'm also currently working on my certification to become a Certified Holistic Nutritionist. This Project is the combination of learning how to live a pure, holistic way of life while also getting a glimpse into my sweaty, energetic and high intense cardio dance classes!
